Nirtox <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/useke2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>seke2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#FF0000>Drinal Ally</font></span><br>  Posts: 401<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/02 5:32:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm35.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: another question</span><hr size=1> the particular situation is that one of my clerics, who has technically been ready to be on the list since april, but was on military duty from april until now (actually back on duty for about 2 more weeks, but then will be back full time), wants to get onto the list, but is a bit frustrated about having to wait 4-5 months despite being ready before most of the people on the list now.  <br>
<br>
